STEP 5 — BLOCKED TASKS (needs human)
════════════════════════════════════════
List every ticket that was excluded because it needs human clarification.

For each:
  ticket_id: [PROJ-XXX]
  blocked_reason: [exactly what information is missing]
  question_to_ask: [the specific question a human needs to answer]
  unblocked_by: [what the human needs to provide — a decision, a design, a link]

These tasks will NOT be passed to the coding agent until a human resolves them.

